OL,3,CDad accuses MOD of 'gross negligence'
OL,4,Cover soldier's military fitness test
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe father of a soldier who died
OL,8,Fduring a military fitness test is
OL,9,Fcalling for the Ministry of Defence
OL,10,F(MoD) to be prosecuted for corporate
OL,11,Fmanslaughter.
OL,13,FPhillip Hoole is heading to Downing
OL,14,FStreet, to submit a petition and
OL,15,Fletter addressed to the Prime Minister.
OL,17,FIt calls for the establishment of a
OL,18,Fnew regulatory body to oversee
OL,19,Finvestigations into institutional
OL,20,Ffailings, like the one he believes has
OL,21,Foccurred in the case of his son.
