OL,3,CDad accuses MOD of 'gross negligence'
OL,4,Cover soldier's military fitness test
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FIn 2016 his son, Joshua, a 26-year-old
OL,8,Farmy corporal from Ecclefechan in
OL,9,FDumfries died whilst taking part in a
OL,10,Ffitness test in the Brecon Beacons.
OL,12,FThe nineteenth of July 2016 was the
OL,13,Fhottest day of that year. Joshua Hoole
OL,14,Fand others were doing an Army Fitness
OL,15,FTest, or AFT; an eight mile march
OL,16,Fcarrying 25 kilograms worth of kit
OL,17,Fthrough the Welsh Hills.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
