OL,4,Cover soldier's military fitness test
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FJust a few hundred metres from its end
OL,8,FJoshua, who was based at Catterick
OL,9,FGarrison and who had previously served
OL,10,Fin Afghanistan and Iraq, collapsed and
OL,11,Fdied.
OL,13,F"For the event they took part in the
OL,14,Fnormal dropout rate is 2.5%," Phillip
OL,15,Ftold ITV News. "On the day that Josh
OL,16,Fdied, the dropout rate was 40%. 18
OL,17,Findividuals out of 40 basically
OL,18,Fdropped out."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
