OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FHe added that some soldiers needed
OL,8,Fmedical attention due to the intense
OL,9,Fheat, but said the test had carried on
OL,10,Fregardless and, he claims, in
OL,11,Fcontravention of army policy at the
OL,12,Ftime.
OL,14,F"The AFT wasn't going to stop for any
OL,15,Freason, not even death," he said.
OL,16,F"Even after my son collapsed and died,
OL,17,Fthe remainder that were left still
OL,18,Ffinished the test."
