OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FPhillip was first told his son had
OL,8,Fdied due to Sudden Adult Death
OL,9,FSyndrome.
OL,11,FBut after fighting for a new inquest,
OL,12,Fa coroner in 2019 concluded that he
OL,13,Fhad died due to a high cardiovascular
OL,14,Fworkload following a combination of
OL,15,Fextreme heat and intense exercise.
OL,17,FIn 2013 the same coroner had carried
OL,18,Fout an inquest into the deaths of
OL,19,Fthree soldiers who died in similar
OL,20,Fcircumstances to Joshua whilst
OL,21,Fattempting SAS selection.
