OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FAfter the inquest into Joshua Hoole's
OL,8,Fdeath, six years later, she said the
OL,9,Farmy had "failed" to learn from
OL,10,Fprevious mistakes, calling this
OL,11,F"deeply concerning."
OL,13,FPhillip says he still does not believe
OL,14,Fhe has got justice for the death of
OL,15,Fhis son, who he believes died as a
OL,16,Fresult of gross negligence on the part
OL,17,Fof the Ministry of Defence (MOD).
OL,19,F"What I'm looking for is an
OL,20,Findependent regulatory body," he said
OL,21,Fof his petition.
